default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultPostal services across the UK face significant challenges from the
default incre
defaultasing use of digital technology;
default the consequential reduction in letter volu
defaultmes and increase in parcel mail;
default 
defaultand the changing needs of users.
default Growth
default in market competition presents 
defaultrisks and opportunities for Royal Mail. Whether in the public or privat
defaulte sector, understanding and responding to consumer needs and changing behaviour will be crucial to effectively competing in the market and sustaining a universal postal service.
